Y" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Ezra-Collective-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Ezra-Collective-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Ezra-Collective-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Ezra-Collective-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Ezra-Collective-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Ezra-Collective-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>自赢得<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/mercury-prize">2023 年水星奖</a>以来， <a href="/artists/ezra-collective">Ezra Collective 的</a>专辑销量和流量增长了近 900%。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ezra-collective-on-their-impact-on-the-jazz-scene-and-plans-to-celebrate-their-mercury-prize-win-3495161">Ezra Collective 谈论他们对爵士乐界的影响并计划庆祝他们获得水星奖</a></strong></li></ul><p>总部位于伦敦的爵士乐队由鼓手兼乐队领队 Femi Koleoso、贝斯手 TJ Koleoso、键盘手 Joe Armon-Jones、小号手 Ife Ogunjobi 和次中音萨克斯管演奏家 James Mollison 组成，凭借他们的第二张唱片《Where I&#39;m Meant To Be》赢得了该奖项”，击败<a href="/artists/loyle-carner">Loyle Carner</a> 、 <a href="/artists/olivia-dean">Olivia Dean</a> 、 <a href="/artists/raye">RAYE</a> 、 <a href="/artists/shygirl">Shygirl</a> 、 <a href="/artists/jockstrap">Jockstrap</a>等。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.thelineofbestfit.com/news/ezra-collective-enjoy-859-album-sales-and-streams-boost-after-winning-mercury-prize" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>The Line of Best Fit</em></a>报道，根据 BPI 对官方排行榜公司数据的分析，《Where I&#39;m Meant To Be》的综合销量和流量增长了 859%。这次跳跃发生在 9 月 8 日至 10 日之间。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/Cw7ntfpK1pK/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0