知道如何创作出色的吉他歌曲，因为我们之前合作过的所有伟大的制作人。只是感觉真的很舒服。”</p><p> “这绝对让人感觉无忧无虑，”麦克托斯蒂补充道，“我仍然对‘如果人们不喜欢它怎么办’或‘如果它被绝对预定怎么办’抱有所有那些古老的不安全感。我关心人们的想法，但不会阻止我做我们想做的事情。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Twin Atlantic - 成名（官方歌词视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/kuZX7_XXVic?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>当 Twin Atlantic 于 2006 年在其他当地乐队的废墟上首次成立时，McTrusty 就已经有了宏伟的计划。他在汉普顿公园体育场附近的一套公寓里长大，从卧室的窗户就能听到<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/acdc">AC/DC</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/red-hot-chili-peppers">Red Hot Chili Peppers</a>等体育场摇滚乐队的演出。</p><p> “我也从不羞于去体育场比赛，”他解释道。 “我对乐队的抱负一直是‘它能有多大？让我们把它做得更大，’知道这是一个不可能的挑战。”</p><p> “我永远不会限制我认为我们能够实现的目标，”他继续说道。 “当我们向 30 人表演第一场演出时，我就想要更多。我只是想通过音乐尽可能多地感受，这一点从未改变。”</p><p>今年晚些时候，Twin Atlantic 将前往英国进行 12 场亲密之旅。 “Maybe it&#39;s a pre-midlife crisis where we want to go back to our teens, touring in a van to places we don&#39;t normally go, but we&#39;re really excited,” said McTrusty. “The shows are going to be fucking amazing and we&#39;re going to give fans an unforgettable night. We&#39;ve been doing this for a minute now and we know how to put on a show. We&#39;re just going to come in and absolutely smash it.”</p><p> Check out the dates below. Tickets are available <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Ftwin-atlantic-tickets%2Fartist%2F1402457" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a> .</p><p> <strong>Twin Atlantic play:</strong></p><p> <strong>November</strong><br /> <strong>13 – Milton Keynes, Crauford Arms</strong><br /> <strong>14 – Lincoln, Drill Hall</strong><br /> <strong>15 – Southend-On-Sea, Chinnerys</strong><br /> <strong>17 – Guildford, Boileroom</strong><br /> <strong>18 – Ipswich, Baths</strong><br /> <strong>19 – Tunbridge Wells, The Forum</strong><br /> <strong>21 – Bournemouth, Old Fire Station</strong><br /> <strong>22 – Hertford, Corn Exchange</strong><br /> <strong>23 – Hull, The Welly</strong><br /> <strong>25 – York, The Crescent</strong><br /> <strong>26 – Blackpool, Bootleg Social</strong><br /> <strong>27 – Chester, Live Rooms</strong></p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/twin-atlantic-new-album-blink-182-intimate-uk-tour-ticket-details-3497826">Twin Atlantic share &#39;Stuck In A Car With You&#39; and tell us about their “unhinged guitar record”</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
